    GH --> GA
    GA --> GA_PROD & GA_REFRESH & GA_SHUTDOWN & GA_O11Y
    
    GA_PROD & GA_REFRESH --> SECRETS
    SECRETS --> ENV
    
    GA_PROD & GA_REFRESH --> BUILD
    BUILD --> DC
    
    ENV --> COMPOSE & DEV_COMPOSE
    ENV --> OTEL
    
    TILT --> BUILD
    TILT --> DC
    
    SCRIPTS --> DC
    
    COMPOSE & DEV_COMPOSE --> DC
    
    DC --> WISBOT & LLM & DB & ADMINER & OTEL_SVC
    
    COMPOSE --> KOMPOSE
    KOMPOSE --> HELM
    HELM --> K8S
    
    K8S --> K8S_WISBOT & K8S_LLM & K8S_DB
    
